HEADWORD: ding-a-ling
<hw>ding"-a-ling</hw> <def>a stupid or foolish person; -- used in a
deprecatory or contemptuous sense.</def> <mark>[slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> dingdong, doofus.</syn>
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

